			.detail
				p I made it easy for people to get addicted to giving this startup all kinds of data while they compare themselves to others.
			.context
				div
					h6.caps My Role:
					p web/UI design
				div
					h6.caps When:
					p summer 2013
				div
					h6.caps With:
					p AKTA, agency

